@startuml
autonumber
skinparam style strictuml
skinparam SequenceMessageAlignment center

participant "AuthenticationFilter" as Filter
participant "ProviderManager\n(AuthenticationManager)" as Manager
participant "DaoAuthenticationProvider\n(Database Expert)" as DaoProvider
participant "JwtAuthenticationProvider\n(JWT Expert)" as JwtProvider
participant "LdapAuthenticationProvider\n(LDAP Expert)" as LdapProvider
database "SecurityContextHolder" as SCH

User -> Filter: Запит з Bearer Token
Filter -> Manager: authenticate(BearerTokenAuthenticationToken)

note over Manager: Manager ітерує список провайдерів

group Цикл по провайдерах
    Manager -> DaoProvider: supports(BearerTokenAuthenticationToken?)
    return false

    Manager -> LdapProvider: supports(BearerTokenAuthenticationToken?)
    return false

    Manager -> JwtProvider: supports(BearerTokenAuthenticationToken?)
    return true
end

note right of JwtProvider: Знайдено потрібний провайдер!

Manager -> JwtProvider: authenticate(BearerToken)
JwtProvider -> JwtProvider: Перевірка підпису JWT\n(Validation)
return Authentication (Authenticated)

Manager --> Filter: Повертає повний Authentication
Filter -> SCH: Зберігає результат у Контекст

@enduml